[color=red][size=18]Spec Racer Ford Challenge Series @ [b] Summit Point Raceway - Full[/b]
Week 9 of 12 - 2017 Season 4 [/size][/color]
Race Distance: [b]18 laps[/b], approximately 25 minutes
World Record lap time: [b]1:21.281[/b] by John Ehlers
(n.b. random/dynamic weather impacts lap times greatly)

For week 9 we're at the venerable Summit Point Raceway. This popular free track provides a great blend of drafting opportunities on the main straight, bravery-testing high speed corners and a slower technical section, making for great racing well suited to the pace of the SRF.

Target "planned" SoF race is usually 20:45 GMT Sunday, immediately following the Weekend Warriors league race.

